__________('price',)__________


Positive Reviews:

---"the volume without the headset is still kind of weak, but quite acceptable with the headset.for the price i'm very happy with the phone." **** 'acceptable'

Negative Reviews:

---'i bought this phone for my wife and after finally getting the mini-sd card for it i\'m relatively impressed.the documentation on the instrument is horrible, but the phone performs well--- as a phone.other features:the mini-sd must be formatted as a vfat partition and there is some restrictions on the primary folder names... "my pictures", "my music"... but after that you can build as many folders as you wish.the photos must be reformatted to a tiny size or the machine will timeout on trying to load them.the media center can build a playlist with all or a subset of your music, and play them randomly selected or in order.the media center controls the volume for all functions (which is sort of silly, but a quick key to media center solves that)this is not a phone for the elitist cellphone user, but is a good starter phone for kids; for a very reasonable price.' **** 'reasonable'


